{
  "title": "Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"position: relative;\"><div alog-group=\"exp-content\" class=\"exp-content format-exp\" id=\"format-exp\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"exp-content-body exp-brief-step\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><div class=\"exp-content-listblock\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div class=\"content-listblock-text\"><p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px;\">如果Eclipse的背景是默认的白色，那么作为程序员，每天持续长时间地盯着屏幕，将会使眼睛非常地疲劳。好在Eclipse提供了免费的主题，可以使我们方便地修改Eclipse的背景，把背景改成暗色的，盯着屏幕也不伤眼睛了。</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-2\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>工具/原料</h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ul class=\"exp-content-unorderlist \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/unsortlist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><div class=\"content-list-text\">Eclipse一个</div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/unsortlist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><div class=\"content-list-text\">可上网电脑一台</div></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-3\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>安装color theme插件</h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ol class=\"exp-conent-orderlist\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 0px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: visible; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">1</div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">打开Eclipse后，在编辑页面。点击help（帮助）——Eclipse Marketplace。</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/4e5b3e195aec8a91901e240c.html?picindex=1\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色\" src=\"quiver-image-url/CAA4A542AC4183A5FF47E767398BAB28.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-2\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: visible; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">2</div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在弹出的窗口中找到搜索框，输入并按Enter搜索color theme，在结果中找到Eclipse Color Theme，点击右下角的install 按钮进行安装。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/4e5b3e195aec8a91901e240c.html?picindex=2\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色\" src=\"quiver-image-url/6E7995F790C08349516336F833A3A17E.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"413\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-3\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: visible; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">3</div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">勾选确认所要安装的插件为Eclipse Color Theme。</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/4e5b3e195aec8a91901e240c.html?picindex=3\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色\" src=\"quiver-image-url/9D1A010934BD0F152F7B83C4B9BE9025.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-4\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: visible; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">4</div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">选择接受协议并点击finish完成安装操作。</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/4e5b3e195aec8a91901e240c.html?picindex=4\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色\" src=\"quiver-image-url/06602A2217B068E95A590A82CDE1CDE2.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"321\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-5\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: visible; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">5</div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">如果出现如下的提示框，提示插件包含未知内容等，点击OK按钮继续完成安装。如果出现需要重启的提示，点击Yes进行重启。</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/4e5b3e195aec8a91901e240c.html?picindex=5\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色\" src=\"quiver-image-url/B5FDAE4ADF3471CC30626CD62F80B223.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"154\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div><div class=\"last-item\" style=\"position: relative; height: 13px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span class=\"last-item-end\" style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 13px; position: absolute; bottom: 0px; left: -48px; display: block;\">END</span></div></li></ol></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-4\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>配置背景颜色</h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ol class=\"exp-conent-orderlist\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 0px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">点击Window——Preferences， 打开偏好设置窗口。</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/4e5b3e195aec8a91901e240c.html?picindex=6\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色\" src=\"quiver-image-url/B5615A6E96BACAC99F72CE95979A0C70.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"485\" height=\"327\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-2\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在右侧依次选择General——Appearance——Color Theme，然后在右边就会显示该插件提供的多个主题，点击选择你想要的主题。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/4e5b3e195aec8a91901e240c.html?picindex=7\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色\" src=\"quiver-image-url/621AC4463362C2C7653864BEBE25D0E4.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"286\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-3\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">选择主题后，右侧可以实时预览设置主题后Eclipse的背景，代码的颜色等样式。如果觉得喜欢主题，则点击Apply（应用）后点击OK按钮将选定的主题应用于Eclipse。</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/4e5b3e195aec8a91901e240c.html?picindex=8\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色\" src=\"quiver-image-url/5166214D8EC7AA88BCB2512B7883A796.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-4\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Eclipse的背景就会被改变了，而且插件会根据代码中的关键字等信息对不同的单词使用不同的颜色，非常漂亮。这是使用前和使用后的Eclipse对比，Color Theme提供了非常丰富的主题库，可以根据自己的喜好进行自由地选择。&nbsp;</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/4e5b3e195aec8a91901e240c.html?picindex=9\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"Eclipse怎样修改背景颜色\" src=\"quiver-image-url/C902359D2F4D17827877D21942A65077.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"320\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div><div class=\"last-item\" style=\"position: relative; height: 13px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span class=\"last-item-end\" style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 13px; position: absolute; bottom: 0px; left: -48px; display: block;\">END</span></div></li></ol></div></div></div><div style=\"clear: both;\"></div></div>"
